Emily Schulman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_Schulman 0 Emily Hope Schulman (born August 17, 1977) is a former child actress and commercial agent, and current acting instructor. She is best known for her role as next-door neighbor Harriet Brindle on the sitcom Small Wonder, which ran from 1985 to 1989.
